snippet: Andy Murray's dominant four-month run ended with a five-set loss to Japan's Kei Nishikori in the quarter-finals of the U.S. Open on Wednesday, but to the Scotsman it was a case of win some, lose some....
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray's dominant four-month run ended with a five-set loss to Japan's Kei Nishikori in the quarter-finals of the U.S. Open on Wednesday, but to the Scotsman it was a case of win some, lose some.

headline.print_headline: Murray Proud of His Stellar Run Despite Defeat
headline.main: Murray Proud of His Stellar Run Despite Defeat
